---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Ushabti">
  <article class="space-y-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-text-dark-primary mb-8">Ushabti</h1>
    <section class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary dark:text-text-dark-secondary leading-relaxed"><strong class="font-semibold text-accent-primary dark:text-accent-dark-primary">A disciplined development framework for AI-assisted code generation</strong></p>
      <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-dark-secondary leading-relaxed">Ushabti is a Claude Code plugin that enforces structured agent-driven development. It implements a rigorous Scribe → Builder → Overseer loop where phases are planned step-by-step, implemented methodically, and reviewed against project laws and style. All state is tracked in plain text files under <code class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">.ushabti/</code>.</p>
      <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-dark-secondary leading-relaxed">The framework is designed to produce correct, maintainable code by enforcing discipline throughout the development lifecycle. Each agent has a clearly defined role and strict boundaries.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-dark-primary">Key Agents</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text-secondary dark:text-text-dark-secondary ml-4">
        <li><strong class="font-semibold text-accent-primary dark:text-accent-dark-primary">Scribe</strong>: Plans phases with detailed steps and acceptance criteria</li>
        <li><strong class="font-semibold text-accent-primary dark:text-accent-dark-primary">Builder</strong>: Implements steps one at a time, updates progress after each step</li>
        <li><strong class="font-semibold text-accent-primary dark:text-accent-dark-primary">Overseer</strong>: Reviews work against laws and style, approves or requests fixes</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-dark-primary">Open Source</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-dark-secondary leading-relaxed">Ushabti is open source and available on GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/adamrdrew/ushabti" class="text-accent-primary dark:text-accent-dark-primary hover:underline">github.com/adamrdrew/ushabti</a></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
